milestones.description: Srinivas Venkataraghavan has broken the record for most ducks (2) in ODIs for IND, going past Syed Kirmani's 1
Wasim Raja has broken the record for most catches (7) in ODIs for PAK, going past Zaheer Abbas's 5
This is the lowest match aggregate (162) involving teams India & Pakistan in ODIs
Srinivas Venkataraghavan has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (8) for IND, going past Madan Lal
Zaheer Abbas and Azmat Rana's 77-run partnership is PAK's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 74 between Majid Khan and Zaheer Abbas
